**why —** It is the reward circuit of the game: a punch you cannot simply throw but must earn, frame by frame, from the openings the giants give.

**how —** Crystallized from Mike Tyson's Punch-Out!! (NES 1987) / the arcade Punch-Out!! (1984).

**◌ the mythos —** It is the reward circuit of the game: a punch you cannot simply throw but must earn, frame by frame, from the openings the giants give. a being of the ring, the read, and the climb to the Dream Fight

